                                                                                                                                  Data and tables

                                                                                                                                  Table

                                                                                                                                  A table is a layout component used to display data in a structured format made up of rows and columns, with each cell containing a piece of data. Tables can present information clearly and organize it, making it easy for users to compare and analyze the data. 

                                                                                                                                  Usage
                                                                                                                                  Specs
                                                                                                                                  Status & changelog


                                                                                                                                  Common alternative names
                                                                                                                                  Add notes

                                                                                                                                  Data array, data grid, information table

                                                                                                                                  Leave a comment in Figma or reach out to us on Slack.

                                                                                                                                  Anatomy


                                                                                                                                  Header row
                                                                                                                                  Add notes

                                                                                                                                  This contains the column headers and labels that describe the data in each column, this element is optional.

                                                                                                                                  Rows
                                                                                                                                  Add notes

                                                                                                                                  the horizontal divisions of the table that contain data.

                                                                                                                                  Columns
                                                                                                                                  Add notes

                                                                                                                                  the vertical divisions of the table that contain data.

                                                                                                                                  Cells
                                                                                                                                  Add notes

                                                                                                                                  the individual boxes where the data is displayed.

                                                                                                                                  Dividers
                                                                                                                                  Add notes

                                                                                                                                  the lines that divides the content. 

                                                                                                                                  Usage

                                                                                                                                  Use a table component when displaying a smaller number of rows or results that have pagination. It includes sorting and row selection features as well as accessibility. Column spans will dynamically size column widths based on content.

                                                                                                                                  The easiest way to use Tables in Base is to use the Base Figma Plugin. This allows you to easily add modify, and change the following properties with a click of a button:

                                                                                                                                  Header

                                                                                                                                  Tables can be displayed with or without a header row

                                                                                                                                  Header: On
                                                                                                                                  Header: Off

                                                                                                                                  Size

                                                                                                                                  This changes the size of the Cell's content.

                                                                                                                                  Size: X Small
                                                                                                                                  Size: Small
                                                                                                                                  Size: Medium

                                                                                                                                  Cell density

                                                                                                                                  Change the vertical spacing of the cell to allow for more or less cells in a certain table height.

                                                                                                                                  Cell density: Compact
                                                                                                                                  Cell density: Default
                                                                                                                                  Cell density: Spacious

                                                                                                                                  Dividers

                                                                                                                                  You can change the divider lines to be displayed on rows, columns, both, or none

                                                                                                                                  Dividers: Row
                                                                                                                                  Dividers: Column
                                                                                                                                  Dividers: Full
                                                                                                                                  Dividers: None

                                                                                                                                  Vertical alignment

                                                                                                                                  This adjusts the vertical alignment of the cell's content

                                                                                                                                  Vertical alignment: Bottom
                                                                                                                                  Vertical alignment: Middle
                                                                                                                                  Vertical alignment: Top

                                                                                                                                  Horizontal alignment

                                                                                                                                  You can also align the content horizontally

                                                                                                                                  Horizontal alignment: Center
                                                                                                                                  Horizontal alignment: Left
                                                                                                                                  Horizontal alignment: Right

                                                                                                                                  Zebra stripes

                                                                                                                                  You can add zebra stripes to your table to alternate the row's background colors, making scanning wider tables easier for your users.

                                                                                                                                  Zebra stripes: Off
                                                                                                                                  Zebra stripes: On

                                                                                                                                  Flushed margins

                                                                                                                                  Sometimes you want to have the table content align with content outside of the table. For this, you can turn the margins on or off

                                                                                                                                  Flushed margins: On
                                                                                                                                  Flushed margins: Off

                                                                                                                                  Table cell presets

                                                                                                                                  The Base Table comes with a set of cell presets. These are the most common table cell types that should cover many scenarios. You can change these by selecting the cells and selecting a preset from the Figma component property panel:

                                                                                                                                  The following presets are available:

                                                                                                                                  Accordion cell
                                                                                                                                  Avatar
                                                                                                                                  Badge cell
                                                                                                                                  Button cell
                                                                                                                                  Checkbox cell
                                                                                                                                  Header cell
                                                                                                                                  Icon cell
                                                                                                                                  Input cell
                                                                                                                                  List cell
                                                                                                                                  Number cell
                                                                                                                                  Radio cell
                                                                                                                                  Tag cell
                                                                                                                                  Text cell

                                                                                                                                  Every preset contains the standard Base components, so you can customize it further like you're used to.

                                                                                                                                  Behavior

                                                                                                                                  Wrapping and truncation

                                                                                                                                  The table contents can wrap or truncate depending on what is appropriate for your use case.

                                                                                                                                  Truncated
                                                                                                                                  Wrapped


                                                                                                                                  Breakpoints

                                                                                                                                  In most cases, the table will take the width of the rest of the content.
